notes:
 This dataset extends DBpedia with more than **3.9 million triples** dealing with **measurement**. For instance the molar heat capacity of a physical element, the voltage of a railway, the speed of a roller coaster and way more. The triples are automatically extracted from Wikipedia infoboxes and the dataset complements DBpedia.

The dataset contains triples such as the following :

http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aswan_Dam

cha:height "111 m"^^cha:measurement  ;

cha:length "3830 m"^^cha:measurement  ;

cha:widthBase "980 m"^^cha:measurement  ;

 cha:annualgeneration "10042 GWh"^^cha:measurement  .
